high_descs: Move to the other side of the counter.
Pick up the gray bowl from the counter.
Bring the bowl to the fridge.
Cool the bowl in the fridge for 3 seconds.
Bring the bowl from the fridge to the wooden shelves.
Put the bowl on the middle shelf on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl on the middle wooden shelf.

high_descs: Walk forward and go around to the opposite side of the counter, where the stools are
Pick up the bowl that's next to a book
Take the bowl over to the fridge
Place the bowl in the middle of the top shelf, close the door, then pick it back up
Take the bowl over to your right, to the book shelf in the left corner, across from the door
Place the bowl down on the second shelf, to the left of the book
anns.task_desc: Grab a bowl, chill it, place it on a shelf

high_descs: Pick up the clear bowl from the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the bowl in it to cool down, and take out the bowl from the fridge.
Place the bowl to the left of the book on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Placed the cooled bowl on the shelf.
